data.description: Amazing unit in Bay Point condominium with third floor primary suite, complete with a full bath, walk-in closet & private balcony. Eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances & pantry. Great room with fireplace & large balcony with storage closet. Two additional bedrooms for guest rooms or use for home office. Located in established waterfront community with access to awesome amenities, including a pool, clubhouse, & tennis courts. Don't miss out on the opportunity to live the ultimate waterfront lifestyle!
